- ğŸ” **Secure Authentication** - JWT certificate-based auth with BNYM Eliza
- ğŸ“Š **Smart Excel Processing** - Automatic Jira field extraction and validation
- ğŸ§ª **BDD Format Generation** - Professional .feature file format output
